    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW M-division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematic integrity, and the exterior retains a flawless finish with uniform paint depth. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, featuring supple Nappa leather and functioning electronics throughout. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
